name: clippings
description:
Digital photo, printed and scanned. Digitally altered, cropped and converted into gif. 

This work is part of the series that includes "la fragmentación", "la caida", "09 perdón" and "11 imágenes 11 impresiones 1 gif". A universe of destruction, time and repetition.

ailen mohh:: 2022:: GIF.:: buenos aires, argentina
